data.description: Well maintained single-level home with great curb appeal and an attached two-car garage located within the highly desirable community of Mesa Valle in San Marcos.  This amazing residence features fully owned solar, neutral paint and trim, central AC, a cozy fireplace, and durable flooring in the main living areas.  An open floorplan with high ceilings basks the home in an abundance of natural light.  A beautifully appointed kitchen with stainless-steel appliances and warm honey-hued cabinetry with an island that opens to the family room.  The spacious primary suite offers exterior patio access, ample closet space, and its own en-suite bathroom.  Outdoor living has been extended to the large backyard with thoughtfully designed hardscape and low maintenance landscaping including orange and lemon trees, making it perfect for entertaining and taking in the views. Conveniently located, just minutes away from parks, great schools, shopping, dining, golf amenities, Highway 78, Interstate 15, plus so much more. Low HOA and No Mello Roos!  Don’t let this opportunity pass you by!
